      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TRUTH TELLER (3) has a strong record this track and trip with three wins and two placings from nine starts. Scored by 1.3 lengths last time (17.02) in a Grade 5 over 300m at Healesville. With a clean break looks hard to beat. ROYAL RUPEE (2) was strongly fancied last time and hit the ground running with a fast early split, giving a sight but fading out of it to finish fourth (22.69) at this track over 390m. Worth following up. STREET SIXTY SIX (4) missed the frame latest when eighth at Horsham (23.86) but scored four back at this track (22.43). Leading chance. PAW JANELLE (7) can sneak into the finish again.",
